{"tid":1662610,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"彭斯下周發表對中国的重要政策演講","createTime":"2019-10-19T01:11:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T01:50:01.000Z","uid":184679,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"166f59c5908f0dcb5eec6775ca925240bcffcb1c","tid":1662610,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T01:11:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1487048_1_20191019021443.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1487048_1_20191019021443.jpg&h=4ee82e2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（美聯社）<br />\n<br />\n路透社引述白宮官員報道，美國副總統彭斯計劃下星期四，發表對中國的第二次重要政策演講。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述這名官員說，過往經常對中國採取鷹派強硬態度的彭斯，將於華盛頓一間酒店發表講話，回顧過去一年的美中關係，並展望未來。<br />\n<br />\n路透社上個月曾經報道，彭斯原定6月發表有關中國的重要講話，推遲到今年較後時間，以免影響中美領導人會晤及中美貿易談判。<br />\n<br />\n彭斯去年在針對中國的演講中，批評中國干預美國內政，意圖令美國換總統，又不斷在南海擴張軍力及打壓台灣，損害台海穩定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1487048-20191019.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1487048-20191019.htm&d=hAhx4mZ6jCiP%2Fv5W8BSz9vrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=f948b942\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1487048-20191019.htm&h=cb3273fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1487048-20191019.htm</a>"},{"pid":"759b41460294a15e2d9b096a7e6e0e058d8e4dce","tid":1662610,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T01:50:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/14/165712_feed9b01dead931da810389bf9455c2c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F14%2F165712_feed9b01dead931da810389bf9455c2c.png&h=4e96cfa2&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}